                                <div class="postmetadata">
					<span class="meta-date"><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/for-advisors-information-csi-updates-and-involvement-fairs-application-is-open/" title="FOR ADVISORS&#8217; INFORMATION: CSI Updates and Involvement Fairs Application is open!" rel="bookmark">
						<span class="month">Aug</span>
						<span class="day">03</span>
						<span class="year">2018</span>
					</a></span>


					

					<span class="meta-author"><span>by jvolpe</span></span>

				</div>
                
				<div class="post-contents">
										<h3 class="entry-title">
					<a href="https://advising.uic.edu/for-advisors-information-csi-updates-and-involvement-fairs-application-is-open/" title="FOR ADVISORS&#8217; INFORMATION: CSI Updates and Involvement Fairs Application is open!" rel="bookmark">FOR ADVISORS&#8217; INFORMATION: CSI Updates and Involvement Fairs Application is open!</a>
					</h3>
                    					    <div class="post-category">Posted in <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advising-weekly-updates/">Advising Weekly Updates</a>, <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/for-advisors-information/">For Advisors' Information</a></div>
                    					<div class="post-content">
					<p><strong>UIC Involvement Fairs</strong><br />
Involvement Fair Applications for Departments &amp; Colleges are now open!</p>
<p>Each year, the Center for Student Involvement hosts an annual “kick off” event for the students, faculty and staff of UIC, to celebrate not only the beginning of the school year, but also to introduce the campus to the many involvement opportunities in the surrounding the UIC community and the city. The Involvement Fair will expose students to the diverse engagement opportunities available at UIC. Over 200 student organizations, university departments, and neighboring businesses will be on hand to greet and welcome students to campus. Involvement Fairs are a part of the Weeks of Welcome!<br />
Wednesday, September 5, 2018 and Thursday, September 6, 2018<br />
11:00 AM – 4:00 PM<br />
Lecture Center Quad</p>
<p>Apply on UIC Connection: <a href="https://uic.campuslabs.com/engage/submitter/form/start/200265">https://uic.campuslabs.com/engage/submitter/form/start/200265</a></p>
<p>Submission of an application does not guarantee a spot at the Involvement Fair; space is limited and granted on a first come-first serve basis. Confirmations will be sent out August 17. If you have specific questions, please feel free to connect with CSI!</p>
<p><strong>NEW Website!</strong><br />
With the help of SA Web Team, CSI has new website and converted to the red platform!  You have no idea how excited we are.  You will see updated information for <strong>Student Organizations, Programs &amp; Events, Fraternity &amp; Sorority Life, and UIC Impact</strong>. Go to <a href="http://involvement.uic.edu/">http://involvement.uic.edu</a> (please clear your history/browser data). Let us know what you think.</p>
<p><strong>UIC Connection</strong><br />
We have successfully migrated our data in UIC Connection into our new platform.  The link to UIC Connection is still the same at <a href="http://connect.uic.edu/">http://connect.uic.edu</a> (please clear your history/browser data). The list of registered student organizations for 2018-2019 is active in UIC Connection.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<br class="clear" />

			</div><!-- end div post -->

		
